<div class="letter-body" style="line-height: 1.8; font-family: 'Noto Sans Devanagari', 'Mangal', sans-serif;">

  <!-- Letterhead -->
  <table style="width:100%; border-bottom: 3px solid #c0392b; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width: 100px; vertical-align: middle;">
        <img src="/logo-bnp.png" alt="Bihar Navodaya Pariwar" style="width: 96px; height: 96px; object-fit: contain;" />
      </td>
      <td style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
        <div style="font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a;">Bihar Navodaya Pariwar</div>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt; color: #555; margin-top: 2px;">
          Flat #204, Aashirwad Residency, Behind Keshav Hospital, Saguna More, Patna, Bihar
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt; color: #555; margin-top: 2px;">
          www.biharnavodayapariwar.com &nbsp;|&nbsp; biharnavodayapariwar@gmail.com
        </div>
      </td>
      <td style="width: 80px;"></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Ref & Date -->
  <table style="width:100%; font-size: 10pt; color: #444; margin-bottom: 16px;">
    <tr>
      <td>Ref: BNP/AUD/2026</td>
      <td style="text-align:right;">Date: 17 March 2026</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Recipient -->
  <p><strong>To,</strong></p>
  <p style="margin: 2px 0;">The Deputy General Manager (HR/Admin),</p>
  <p style="margin: 2px 0;">Bihar State Power Holding Company Limited, Patna.</p>

  <br/>

  <!-- Subject -->
  <p>
    <strong>Subject:</strong> Regarding reservation of Urja Auditorium Hall.
  </p>

  <br/>

  <p><strong>Sir / Madam,</strong></p>

  <p style="text-align: justify;">
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We wish to inform you that <strong>Bihar Navodaya Pariwar</strong> is an active and organized platform of former students of all Jawahar Navodaya Vidyalayas in the state of Bihar. The organization works towards bringing together alumni of Jawahar Navodaya Vidyalayas from across the state and establishing coordination among them.
  </p>

  <p style="text-align: justify;">
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In this regard, <strong>"Bihar Navodayan Samagam 5.0 (Alumni Meet / Exhibition)"</strong> is being organized, which is the annual gathering of all Navodayans. Members of Navodaya Pariwar from various districts of Bihar participate in this event. The said programme is scheduled on <strong>5 April 2026</strong> from <strong>8:00 AM</strong> to <strong>8:30 PM</strong>. Therefore, you are kindly requested to reserve the Urja Auditorium Hall for the said event.
  </p>

  <p style="text-align: justify;">
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We humbly request you to kindly allot the venue for the above programme.
  </p>

  <br/>
  <br/>

  <!-- Signature -->
  <p style="text-align: right;">Yours faithfully,</p>
  <br/>
  <p style="text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Gagan Gaurav</strong></p>
  <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 2px;">Coordinator, Bihar Navodaya Pariwar</p>
  <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 2px;">Contact: 9304619105</p>

</div>
